OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'on brink of resigning'
OL,4,Cas Andy Burnham returns to Westminster
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer is facing increased
OL,7,Fpressure to resign as prime minister
OL,8,Fas Andy Burnham is expected to make
OL,9,Fhis return to Westminster on Monday.
OL,11,FBurnham is due to be sworn in as
OL,12,FMakerfield's MP, after winning
OL,13,FThursday's by-election and increasing
OL,14,FLabour's share of the vote in the
OL,15,Fconstituency by 9.61%
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
