OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782146887
OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'on brink of resigning'
OL,4,Cas Andy Burnham returns to Westminster
OL,6,FThe prime minister, who is reported to
OL,7,Fhave spent the weekend mulling his
OL,8,Fpolitical future, is said to have been
OL,9,Ftold by members of his Cabinet,
OL,10,Fincluding Foreign Secretary Yvette
OL,11,FCooper, that he should set out a
OL,12,Ftimetable for his departure.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
