OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782146887
OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'on brink of resigning'
OL,4,Cas Andy Burnham returns to Westminster
OL,6,FA spokesperson for No 10 said
OL,7,FStarmer's position remained unchanged
OL,8,Ffrom Friday, when he said he will not
OL,9,F"walk away" from Downing Street and
OL,10,Fwill stand in any potential contest.
OL,12,F"There's more to do, and that's what
OL,13,FI'm focused on, what I was elected to
OL,14,Fdo, which is to serve my country,"
OL,15,FStarmer said on Friday.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
