PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782146887
OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'on brink of resigning'
OL,4,Cas Andy Burnham returns to Westminster
OL,6,FOn Sunday, Business Secretary Peter
OL,7,FKyle did not shut down questions about
OL,8,FStarmer's future as he spoke to
OL,9,Fbroadcasters and said the PM was
OL,10,Ftaking time to "think through what the
OL,11,Fpolitical realities are today compared
OL,12,Fto last week, the week before".
OL,14,F"I don't know the decisions that he
OL,15,Fwill make on behalf of our country",
OL,16,FKyle said, adding that "whatever
OL,17,Funfolds" in the coming days will be a
OL,18,F"functional process".
