OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782146887
OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'on brink of resigning'
OL,4,Cas Andy Burnham returns to Westminster
OL,6,FBurnham made it clear in his
OL,7,FMakerfield speech that he hoped his
OL,8,Felection would be a "turning point"
OL,9,Fand that he hoped to "lead by example,
OL,10,Ffrom the front" to bring about
OL,11,Fnational change.
OL,13,FQuestions are being raised within
OL,14,FLabour about how a change of leader
OL,15,Fwould come about ` with some backing a
OL,16,Fleadership contest, and others a swift
OL,17,Ftransfer of power to Burnham.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
