OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'on brink of resigning'
OL,4,Cas Andy Burnham returns to Westminster
OL,6,FReports suggest Burnham is hoping for
OL,7,Faround a month's handover, giving
OL,8,FStarmer time to get his Defence
OL,9,FInvestment Plan over the line in time
OL,10,Ffor the upcoming Nato summit.
OL,12,FIt would mean Starmer could also sign
OL,13,Fhis planned EU co-operation deal at
OL,14,Fthe second annual reset summit with
OL,15,Fthe bloc in July.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
