OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'on brink of resigning'
OL,4,Cas Andy Burnham returns to Westminster
OL,6,FFormer health secretary Wes Streeting
OL,7,Fdeclared his intention to stand in any
OL,8,Fleadership race after he resigned from
OL,9,FStarmer's Cabinet in May, but there is
OL,10,Fspeculation he could instead join
OL,11,FBurnham's cabinet.
OL,13,FStreeting, who has called the decision
OL,14,Fto leave the EU a "catastrophic
OL,15,Fmistake", has pledged to adopt a
OL,16,F"maximalist" approach to forging
OL,17,Fcloser ties with the bloc.
OL,26,@vD@SOUwD@HO]xD@AOUxD@LO]
