OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'on brink of resigning'
OL,4,Cas Andy Burnham returns to Westminster
OL,6,F"Keir Starmer will resign as Prime
OL,7,FMinister of The United Kingdom. He
OL,8,Ffailed badly on two very important
OL,9,Fsubjects ` IMMIGRATION AND ENERGY
OL,10,F(OPEN NORTH SEA OIL!). I wish him
OL,11,Fwell!" the president said.
OL,13,FTrump has not spoken to Starmer since
OL,14,Fthe leaders saw each other at the G7
OL,15,Fsummit in France earlier this week,
OL,16,Faccording to reports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
